summary: Confident, proactive, hands-on and results driven professional with over 7 years of experience in Academic Publishing. Recognized talent for management of people and projects even in times of pressure. Enthusiastic in working with a team while always keeping a perceptive eye on organizational objectives and goals. Organizational skills combined with proactive attitude have led to an independent and dependable work ethic when given the responsibility. Team player with a helicopter view.
